commentary: Muzarabani to Tamim Iqbal, 1 no ball full and wide outside off, goes over the tram lines through to the keeper. Tamim misses the wild slog, but another big no ball from the debutant. The free hit continues.

commentary: Muzarabani to Tamim Iqbal, 2 runs back of a length on leg stump, tapped off his hips to deep backward square. They want the second, and Tamim may be out here! Direct hit from the man at deep backward square, but replays suggest he's in.
